            "notes": "The main concept of this deck is to utilize the powerful abilities of Spider-Man 2099 as the commander to lead an aggro strategy. The deck includes a mix of control elements and efficient creatures and spells to put pressure on the opponent and disrupt their game plan. With cards like True-Name Nemesis and Malcolm, Alluring Scoundrel, the deck aims to establish a strong board presence while using counter spells like Counterspell and Force of Negation to protect its threats. Additionally, cards like Lightning Bolt and Pyrokinesis provide direct damage to finish off opponents quickly. The deck focuses on quick and efficient plays to overwhelm opponents and secure a victory in a 1 vs 1 Duel Commander game."
